Pacioli – Core Prototype Features
✅ What It Does
Position Awareness
Player & entity positions
Cached and consistent
Distance & Radius Logic
Fast proximity checks
Minimal redundant calculations
State Tracking
Health (basic)
Movement flags (future)
Consistency Layer
Deterministic outputs
No jitter or inconsistent logic

❌ What It Does NOT Do
UI elements (no screens, overlays, title cards)
Items or blocks (no world modification)
Boss-specific logic or AI behaviors
Fancy physics (PID, impulses, angular momentum, etc.)